INSERT INTO queue_tasks (
            task_id, run_id, state_name, task_payload, status,
            attempts, max_attempts, error_message, last_error_at, next_retry_at,
            queued_at, processing_at, completed_at, failed_at,
            created_at, updated_at
        ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
